{"tid":1690834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈要同左膠宣戰","createTime":"2019-11-03T12:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T13:42:30.000Z","uid":150983,"like":40,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7e9fc400b45d60163c07a640936a5dcd571fd4d8","tid":1690834,"uid":150983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死左膠，你知唔知私了唔到班仆街斬人藍絲有幾大禍害？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母你估班狗會入佢哋數？陣間放返出嚟又斬多幾個手足點撚算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你知唔知你拎光環嘅背後講緊會有幾個手足可能因為咁而冇命同殘廢，你哋賠唔賠得起？<br />\n<br />\n以後你班左膠係都要保護有威脅性藍絲嘅，唔好怪我哋拎你哋嚟祭旗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正你地保護得班藍絲，就即係增家緊手足們遇害嘅風險，同敵人冇分別。"},{"pid":"3f41426a3e14855fd43b0fd97e5457e09c947416","tid":1690834,"uid":150983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:29:46.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"86ec860b8e29114cb637fba91ed0e520e8d3f23a","tid":1690834,"uid":150983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"08d540061b97d4d5ab11fc9caaac15b799d98ef5","tid":1690834,"uid":150983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:30:07.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"ddb11bde917393758aa6ca90c336b85d43f5bad6","tid":1690834,"uid":59357,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:30:09.000Z","msg":"班左膠又會話你5毛 唔明你屌緊乜 笑撚死 香港由回歸到宜家都係衰係左膠手上"},{"pid":"3194f592a5395c340b35069862922df101c5b872","tid":1690834,"uid":148253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:30:24.000Z","msg":"曱近平"},{"pid":"441295723f3762a39f0807ad10e8317e5701ddff","tid":1690834,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:30:33.000Z","msg":"唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/